{
  "stem": "12029.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was looking after her quite well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She used to learn like to go-- she didn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I don't think there were schools.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she used to go to a teacher to learn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she used even to learn to play piano.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Yes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then we were-- [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] and we were there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was Christmas.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then when it was getting warm, I didn't feel well.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I couldn't catch the breath.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then Arnold decided that I've got to get a place, that I should look after children or something to be in fresh.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That Pole had two little children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I went there, left them, my mother and Arnold.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I went to that Pole to look after the children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But at night, I used to go to that woman, where [INAUDIBLE] was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But she-- [INAUDIBLE] was already in the country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then I slept there at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And in the morning, I used to go back to my work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "One day, I went there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And on the way, in the evening, she followed me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I went on the tram.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I saw that she's-- and there were two trams.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "One was for the Poles and was for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This old woman went on the tram for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she was showing them-- and I saw it on a distant-- that I was there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I run down from the tram.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I hid in a block of flats there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And when I saw that she left, I went to that Polish woman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as I was walking to the Polish woman, I met the blackmailer who blackmailed me before.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
